{"tid":1502492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳雲：誰建議召開調查委員會，誰參加大台，那人就是賣港賊。","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T06:18:53.000Z","uid":2748,"like":134,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"578b4d5cd879cbe6a9c015944c15bb3873988ba0","tid":1502492,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"陳雲：今日警察又亂開槍，射擊與他們罵戰的街坊。誰建議召開調查委員會，誰參加大台，那人就是賣港賊。香港目前政府領導警察、公共交通公司、黑幫一齊壓迫人民，警察無故向市民施暴及中共向香港企業政治迫害，已經達到戰爭罪行的狀態，那是對話大台或調查委員會無法有權威和能力解決的。香港必須等到普選修憲之後，便有權審判犯法的警察、官員，並驅逐不受歡迎的公共組織總裁。一旦香港被逼採用革命方式建國的話，以人民法庭或軍事法庭的方式，權宜行事。<br />\n這是顯而易見的簡單道理，如果有人詐作不知，仍建議組織大台來對話，那人就是賣港賊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68756697_10157359613372225_4084691250580553728_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_eui2=AeERCCjiiPSyKDo4p1zi5XjwYmyJ1Rb3eJ6Last9GqUl2umMaYPJR39DdLSmQqpmg86jcHVvts-Um_ootV3NgNu803bnZGtuZ_3-sZ_0OqgOVA&amp;_nc_oc=AQmI51MIqgzbZItjCENaz3kFjJ_cgj6uGDDzxX04d7vDyotDDU_7j_kThjOe_pRM4t0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=5b0c55b4bd4bfd6a9dd0b37f5cef8fa9&amp;oe=5DC85451\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68756697_10157359613372225_4084691250580553728_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_eui2%3DAeERCCjiiPSyKDo4p1zi5XjwYmyJ1Rb3eJ6Last9GqUl2umMaYPJR39DdLSmQqpmg86jcHVvts-Um_ootV3NgNu803bnZGtuZ_3-sZ_0OqgOVA%26_nc_oc%3DAQmI51MIqgzbZItjCENaz3kFjJ_cgj6uGDDzxX04d7vDyotDDU_7j_kThjOe_pRM4t0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D5b0c55b4bd4bfd6a9dd0b37f5cef8fa9%26oe%3D5DC85451&h=19b7d984&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"772a96ecb7e71e620697ce9f9ea1b34c91d92385","tid":1502492,"uid":224479,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190823/s00001/1566538736816/%E3%80%8C%E5%92%8C%E7%90%86%E5%90%8C%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8D%E7%B1%B2%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8-%E5%BE%85%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%E7%89