lor: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">身份證</span></strong></span>同八達通。<br />\n如果有巴打執到，麻煩call 一call 92451725，感謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩當日在場既義士幫幫手傳一傳開去，因為比POPO執到都幾大獲，唔該各位！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bfe6496cb7e8b5115317989e15e6a59da0be4e","tid":1502492,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf09c4854ecec8dc7ecaec949f438a3e0d41ba2","tid":1502492,"uid":42431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815bc5cc8fc0a0989079574b62f5932003d7d0eb","tid":1502492,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90494cf0a12bb235a45265aa29035a32446abd6a","